        <a class="wordmark" href="/"><span class="glyph" aria-hidden="true">K</span><span>Koru</span></a>
        <p>Writing memory for your Mac. Free to download, local by design.</p>
      </div>
      <nav class="footer-cols" aria-label="Footer navigation">
